data.text:
11th District of Michigan

Michigan's 11th Congressional District encompasses Oakland County.

Major cities include Auburn Hills, Berkley, Birmingham, Bloomfield Twp, Bloomfield Hills, Clawson, Commerce Twp, Farmington, Farmington Hills, Ferndale, Hazel Park, Huntington Woods, Lake Angelus, Madison Heights, Oak Park, Orchard Lake Village, Pleasant Ridge, Pontiac, Royal Oak, Royal Oak Twp, Sylvan Lake, Troy, Walled Lake, Waterford, West Bloomfield Twp, White Lake Twp, Wixom, and Wolverine Lake.

Not sure if you live in Michigan's 11th District? Click here.

If you are looking for our District Office contact information, you can view our Offices page. If you have any questions, feel free to email us.
